arStrings.szText: Thank Akarat for you... I'd shake your hand, but my arm, you see... We were on our way to Tarsarak when that demon attacked.
Wounded/in pain. (arm bitten by demon) Relieved to see Player.
(chuckle) I was lucky, to a point... I managed to slay one of the creatures, but it got its fangs in me. The venom... is not pleasant.
Wounded/in pain, downplaying both. Putting on a brave face.
I need a flower to treat it... the ghost palm. It grows near those old bones. Bring one back to me, would you?
Wounded/in pain, downplaying both. Putting on a brave face.
